Sooooooo, 'and' [i:14onx03d]can [/i:14onx03d]be used with regular if scripts, without having to resort to flags??

[code:14onx03d]if Got objectA (give location description minus objectA)
if Got objectB (give location description minus objectB)
if Got objectA and objectB (give location description minus both objects)
else (give location description including both objects)[/code:14onx03d]
Makes far more sense than the complicated stack of ifs I had to use.
